# Objective

Perform functional testing on a user registration feature by verifying that the application behaves according to its requirements. Record the expected and actual results for each test scenario.

---

# Feature Under Test

User Registration

The application allows new users to create an account using:

- Full Name
- Email Address
- Password
- Confirm Password

### Functional Requirements

- All fields are required.
- Email addresses must be unique.
- Password must contain at least 8 characters.
- Password and Confirm Password must match.
- Successful registration redirects the user to the dashboard.

